etic wave and by standing magnetic wave in an\nIsing ferromagnet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 May 2016 16:15:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 16 Jul 2016 08:25:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-08"}
