ussion identifies remaining challenges\nto be addressed in future development of electronic structure methods, for\nwhich the here presented benchmark database may serve as an important\nreference.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 May 2016 23:05:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-05"}
