his framework simply by calculating the J-V characteristic\nwith an absorption spectrum. Finally, we expand our SLME analysis to indirect\nband gap absorbers by studying silicon, and find that the SLME quickly\noverestimates the reverse saturation current of indirect band gap materials,\ndrastically lowering their calculated efficiency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 May 2016 12:48:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Jun 2016 13:24:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-05"}
